# Auto-load this worktree's devenv environment via direnv.
#
# Requires direnv + devenv installed (see docs/development/setup.md). Run
# `direnv allow` once per worktree to authorize it; thereafter `cd` into the
# worktree loads the toolchain, per-worktree ports, and runs guarded first-run
# setup with no manual `devenv shell`.
eval "$(devenv direnvrc)"
use devenv
